{"tid":912804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國非洲豬瘟疫情惡化快速    北京淪陷了","createTime":"2018-11-23T03:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T01:49:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2ca61eca148a18004cafa4ef167f6f9cf3569f","tid":912804,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:09:42.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國爆發非洲豬瘟，疫情越來越惡化，一向管控嚴格的首都北京市，也爆出疫情，已死86頭染病豬隻。<br />\n<br />\n中國農業農村部上午發出訊息，證實北京市房山區排查出非洲豬瘟疫情；指今天上午接到中國動物疫病預防控制中心報告，確診北京市房山區青龍湖鎮、琉璃河鎮各一個養殖場排查出非洲豬瘟疫情。截至目前，青龍湖鎮某養殖場存欄生豬1325頭，死亡49頭；琉璃河鎮養殖場存欄生豬429頭，死亡37頭。<br />\n<br />\n疫情發生後，已啟動啟動應急機制，採取封鎖、撲殺、無害化處理、消毒等處置措施，對全部病死和撲殺豬進行無害化處理。同時，禁止所有生豬及其產品調出封鎖區，禁止生豬運入封鎖區。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，中國非洲豬瘟已擴散逾半中國省市，至今仍在惡化當中，對當地農地及經濟都產生嚴重後果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2621681\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2621681&d=GjAYn5dUZSke43U%2BKahIaV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=66452662\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2621681&h=f8a634ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2621681</a>"},{"pid":"0f7265a5edfad0bd29ac5b03a5442df0a23771fa","tid":912804,"uid":10056,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:12:26.000Z","msg":"病死豬對人體無害可食用"},{"pid":"98fa0c54b9e16a1939bbdcb1ca06650894f55adb","tid":912804,"uid":155137,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:13:00.000Z","msg":"點解香港官員唔叫市民提高警覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2858cb08dbf9be1646315ccf6f5d3c4340a6ea3a","tid":912804,"uid":1070,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:14:27.000Z","msg":"屍殺列車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7164aa749deac93afaec9678c41351c9d0156988","tid":912804,"uid":54373,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTi